Avoid #define TF_XLA_HAS_SSE4_1 1 and just have #define TF_XLA_HAS_SSE4_1: I have done this part.


Putting all of these definitions (TF_XLA_HAS_*) in a single header: I gave the explanation why I did not follow this comment.



